absolute_magnetization.description: Absolute magnetization (i.e. integration over space of the absolute value of the local magnetization) of the 2D monolayer, per unit cell

abundance.description: Abundance on the Earth of the rarest of the elements present in the compound

band_gap.description: Electronic band gap of the 2D monolayer

binding_energy_per_substructure_per_unit.description: Binding energy of the bulk 3D, per 2D layer and per unit area, obtained with vdW-DF2-C09 functional
Binding energy of the bulk 3D, per 2D layer and per unit area, obtained with vdW-rVV10 functional

delta_df2.description: Relative difference in the interlayer distance, between vdW-DF2-C09 and revPBE functionals

delta_rvv10.description: Relative difference in the interlayer distance, between vdW-rVV10 and revPBE functionals

fermi_energy.description: Fermi energy(ies) of the 2D monolayer (there can be two of them for magnetic materials)

total_magnetization.description: Total magnetization (i.e. integration over space of the local magnetization) of the 2D monolayer, per unit cell
